    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the high-revving S54 powerplant, featuring a flawlessly maintained VANOS system and individual throttle bodies. The chassis is structurally sound with a reinforced rear subframe, while the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement. Every mechanical component, from the variable M differential lock to the factory-spec suspension bushings, remains in peak operational condition. With documented valve clearances and a pristine cooling system, this vehicle offers the visceral performance of a naturally aspirated straight-six in its most refined state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
