      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it is in flawless condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014no scratches, no dings, and the interior still smells brand new. It drives like a dream and has been meticulously cared for. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and see it for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
