      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring OEM-spec bushings for uncompromising turn-in precision. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with mechanical certainty, complemented by a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. This vehicle exhibits flawless paint depth and an interior devoid of common bolster wear or pixel degradation. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically preserved, it represents a turn-key opportunity for the serious driver.",
